                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Juwel: I'm posting a response to Paroxysmus9 here as I understood you wanted responses in the "canceled my account" thread to be limited there, and new threads to be made in response to commentary outside.  If this is considered a rant, please move it to rants.
